title: Base Contract - Schedule Endpoint - Games - Tied - 2016 Tied Games
custom_steps: WHEN user executes a GET request to https://statsapi.mlb.com/api/v1/schedule/games/tied?season=2016 with the Season parameter
custom_expected: THEN the returned JSON object adheres to the Pact.IO consumer contract

title: Base Contract - Standings Endpoint - 2020 MLB Regular Season Standings
custom_steps: WHEN user executes a GET request to https://statsapi.mlb.com/api/v1/standings?season=2020&leagueId=103,104&standingsTypes=regularSeason with the Season, LeagueId, and StandingsTypes parameters
